headline: Analyst bullish on Texas Instruments on earnings lift as capex winds down
summary: Investing.com -- Wolfe Research upgraded Texas Instruments (NASDAQ:TXN) to Outperform from Peer Perform on Monday, saying the chipmaker is nearing the end of a heavy investment cycle that had weighed on margins and free cash flow.
